      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "276ca72edeac9a23",
      "text": "# Future Development note\nThe business proposal naturally falls into two parts - which will be intertwined at the outset, but become more separate as the project scales.\n1. The currency platform and markets\n1. The development of platform tools\nWe should be clear that we understand this and predict this increasing distinction.\nSuggest that there are two names:\n# ecommony \nand\n# platform.earth"
